Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好怀念的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚后去大坂三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈去九州已经十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妈爸现在还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最近没联系过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,久美 你偶尔有和他们联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像蛮好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在完全变成一个农家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过突然地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说什麽要去九州搞农业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在都市裡好好生活不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏去搞农业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸是不是农耕民族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就只知道工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,相比之下，久美就是狩猎民族了 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为才看到你找男友,马上就结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,都没见过那个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正好有件事想拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是钱的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子几个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,5个月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那样没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是要我们照顾孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事我怎麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都澴没说结婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都没男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你别多说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想要去修养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要是妈妈在的话更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候我老公转过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都在大坂买了房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,公司裡工资也不高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还要很多费用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想让他在这里住一段时间 不知道可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住这？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊.这有什麽好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子还是爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是不要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个每个月给10万日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和爸爸商量过了.没关係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还要照顾妹妹的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且都没i见过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,同一屋檐下争夺年轻男性的二熟女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是小敦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小敦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事.太欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有点心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小敦好年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,几岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,33啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,14年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,17年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,久美也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,两位其实看著根年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是已经
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,两位都很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就当这裡是自己家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把我当做久美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,房间还没准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,二楼裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去把行李放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,舞香姐，仁羑姐都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,又年轻又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感费好幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好多水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,吵到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不..没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚几点回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,吃肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,房间的起味都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,久美好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且接下来半年他都一个人 很容易出轨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让他出轨
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.07,1:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.87,1:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.90,1:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这麽直
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.97,1:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌头来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.88,1:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.82,1:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.29,1:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.77,1:08:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这麽多
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.57,1:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这麽多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.71,1:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这裡都有
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.71,1:08:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你舔乾?淨
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.36,1:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那麽准备出发吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.45,1:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.72,1:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我和两位姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.65,1:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,产生了不可以的关係
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.48,1:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.34,1:29:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.88,1:29:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.35,1:30:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.75,1:30:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.17,1:30:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,证明你爱我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.24,1:30:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,证明给我看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.08,1:31:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.81,1:31:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.55,1:31:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.65,1:32:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你看怎麽样了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.46,1:32:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.39,1:32:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.40,1:32:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.14,1:32:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.57,1:33:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流的磬音
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.93,1:33:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,突然插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.20,1:33:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.42,1:33:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去.插进去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.16,1:33:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.24,1:34:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.94,1:34:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻男人真好
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.50,1:35:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.24,1:35:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.79,1:35:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要丢了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.01,1:35:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让我也来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.41,1:36:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拔掉.不要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.29,1:36:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.65,1:36:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.97,1:37:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好坏啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.77,1:37:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.32,1:37:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.93,1:37:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.55,1:38:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.35,1:38:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.04,1:38:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.78,1:38:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,求你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.05,1:38:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.93,1:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.13,1:39:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.26,1:39:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我都这麽湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.54,1:39:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自己弄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.87,1:39:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小敦 小敦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.42,1:39:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是我的好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.03,1:39:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.24,1:39:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.51,1:39:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还没进来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.38,1:40:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.79,1:40:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.93,1:40:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还没进去
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.24,1:40:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.25,1:41:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还是这麽硬
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.31,1:42:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看你的证明
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.44,1:42:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用力用力
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.56,1:42:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小敦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.04,1:43:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.78,1:43:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.40,1:43:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.56,1:44:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.09,1:44:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以射
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.19,1:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.89,1:45:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.43,1:45:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,动超来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.97,1:45:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.78,1:45:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要大鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.30,1:46:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.37,1:46:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经够了吧 才没有
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.31,1:46:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.78,1:46:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.32,1:46:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.53,1:46:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把腰抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.81,1:47:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,用力插
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.77,1:47:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我选不了 选不了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.25,1:47:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.66,1:48:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以射
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.42,1:48:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拔掉
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.22,1:48:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过爱我的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.16,1:48:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.17,1:48:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.38,1:48:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.31,1:49:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.98,1:49:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,丢了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.73,1:50:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.87,1:50:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.43,1:50:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.38,1:51:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.85,1:51:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想做到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.97,1:51:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了，要射要射
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.37,1:52:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这裡.射这裡
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.73,1:52:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让你舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.58,1:53:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.58,1:53:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,澴想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.27,1:53:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还那样吸
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.21,1:53:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.35,1:53:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.22,1:54:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.12,1:54:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,半年后
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.86,1:54:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后我被搾乾
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.46,1:54:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,终于去九州接了久美
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.60,1:54:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在东京的八王子住下了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.54,1:54:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,半年后
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.74,1:54:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有了孩子后第一次再去见姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.02,1:55:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.15,1:55:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐在家吗
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.50,1:55:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你们两个
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.57,1:55:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.57,1:55:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怀上了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.51,1:55:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.78,1:55:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为不行呢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.33,1:55:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,圆城仁美
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.47,1:55:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,浅井舞香